an affirmative response.

7
00:00:30.166 --> 00:00:33.094 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[theme music]

8
00:02:00.120 --> 00:02:01.204 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
