00:17:51.904 --> 00:17:53.447 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[chatting]

282
00:17:53.739 --> 00:17:58.411 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
