<i>he chose to become a hero.</i>

286
00:18:11.382 --> 00:18:13.551 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<i>And now he's ready</i>
<i>to reveal the reason.</i>

287
00:18:14.719 --> 00:18:15.761 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Barnaby!

288
00:18:15.928 --> 00:18:18.264 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>You may not have noticed, but he's</i>
<i>the only hero</i>

289
00:18:18.431 --> 00:18:20.600 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
