00:19:06.979 --> 00:19:10.524 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
War against the man who
killed his parents twenty years ago.

302
00:19:13.819 --> 00:19:14.945 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Is that for real?

303
00:19:15.029 --> 00:19:16.989 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
I never knew that was his
background.

304
00:19:17.323 --> 00:19:19.283 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
No wonder he's so
committed to justice.

305
00:19:19.617 --> 00:19:22.787 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>And now... he's finally found that man.</i>

306
00:19:23.037 --> 00:19:25.873 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
