307
00:19:25.998 --> 00:19:27.833 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>when he was just a child of four.</i>

308
00:19:27.958 --> 00:19:31.462 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
