316
00:20:03.661 --> 00:20:04.912 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
[cheering]
You can do it Barnaby!

317
00:20:05.162 --> 00:20:06.956 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[crowd cheering]

318
00:20:07.164 --> 00:20:09.041 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
