320
00:20:18.551 --> 00:20:20.594 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
So that's why he's been so dedicated.

321
00:20:20.928 --> 00:20:24.306 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
