our friend Barnaby, if nothing else.

322
00:20:26.976 --> 00:20:27.977 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>It's me...</i>

323
00:20:28.185 --> 00:20:29.103 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Origami?

324
00:20:29.186 --> 00:20:33.023 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>Yes. And I need to report,</i>
