325
00:20:33.190 --> 00:20:34.066 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[gasping]

326
00:20:34.191 --> 00:20:36.235 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Great job, champ.
