328
00:20:38.654 --> 00:20:41.323 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>I've got to find the secret</i>
<i>behind those powered exosuits!</i>

329
00:20:41.657 --> 00:20:43.617 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Watch your back at all times, Origami.

330
00:20:43.826 --> 00:20:46.120 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Return safely, and I'll
